===Etymology===
Alteration of [[curtal]], from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|courtault||which has been shortened}}, itself from {{m|fro|court||short}} (from {{etyl|la|en}} [[curtus]]) + {{m|la||-ault}}

